{"url": "https://people.com/tv/long-island-medium-theresa-caputo-faces-ex-larry-after-split/", "text": "Theresa Caputo is adjusting to her new life after splitting from her husband Larry Caputo.\n\nIn PEOPLE\u2019s exclusive look at the upcoming new season of Long Island Medium, the former couple comes face-to-face for the first time since announcing their separation last year.\n\n\u201cWe separated about a year ago and so I haven\u2019t physically seen Larry in like, nine months,\u201d Theresa says in the clip.\n\nAs the two sit down at a restaurant to talk, Larry admits that seeing his ex is harder than he expected.\n\n\u201cIt\u2019s not easy,\u201d says Larry. \u201cAfter 30-plus years \u2014 how do you not have emotions?\u201d\n\nTheresa is also faced with the harsh reality of having to experience life on her own for the first time in nearly three decades. After tearing her ACL, the medium undergoes her first major surgery.\n\n\u201cIt was weird waking up and Larry not being there,\u201d she says. \u201cBut this is our new life.\u201d\n\nTheresa and Larry announced their separation in Dec. 2017 after 28 years of marriage. They share two adult children: Larry Jr., and Victoria.\n\nIn a joint statement to PEOPLE, the TLC stars said, \u201cAfter 28 years of marriage, we have decided to legally separate. We will always love each other and our two wonderful children. We are united in supporting each other and our family. Please respect our privacy during this time.\u201d\n\nRELATED VIDEO: Theresa Caputo Files for Divorce from Husband Larry After 28 Years of Marriage\n\nTheresa, 52, officially filed for divorce on April 16. At the time, she Theresa told Extra that the two were living on opposite coasts \u2014 he in L.A., and she in New York \u2014 and were taking their relationship and the possibility of a reconciliation \u201cday by day.\u201d\n\nLast month, Larry revealed that he\u2019s in a new relationship since splitting from Theresa.\n\n\u201cI have moved on,\u201d he told TMZ. \u201cI\u2019m fortunate enough to say that I have met someone special. But I\u2019ll just leave it for that now.\u201d\n\nLong Island Medium returns for season 13 on Oct. 8 at 8 p.m. ET on TLC.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/PA0UAIbqVPcS7LGhgQkjsDpnQ6Q=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Khloe-Kardashian-110725-tout-304851eeb65b42f5a365c6ae9f0a58f5.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/6YMkmjVi3TmowFGegJCAptVBPY4=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Amy-Schumer-Chris-Fischer-111325-68d54c198ba54698b5d309804bf32f3e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/M29-4Mb1hIFvMalEsMbrXwWxBh8=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/gerry-turner-theresa-nist-110325-86c90e87b4d841a39bf2b243efb8cad1.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/LztNjwaQ-ix4eK4edUooLhNiWi4=/800x533/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/anna-kepner-3-111025-c6a90b2f57474459a89ae04e296ec343.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/nyP-nh5D6JXa7aD3yEiHmqNbnto=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/keith-urban-nicole-kidman-2023-cma-100125-a2de2d6a517a43639e53b558baab1bc7.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/hrpIf_Ds6fRnwyzQj3Z_T0v7wRw=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/alex-rodriguez-Cynthia-Scurtis-Madonna-111325-33c2de3e05914ed987d94df4aced2d95.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/6BVgFQ30gWgD9XmkUm2j5s90DZk=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/alex-rodriguez-Cynthia-Scurtis-Madonna-111325-33c2de3e05914ed987d94df4aced2d95.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/k9H3hWHcWWkuAIhDYdaGUeRk2vU=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Kim-Kardashian-111025-07cc4d18060a4af089bb4b0e12e75c44.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/wvmIeAcYNWOEwncYIejtu3NqDfg=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/brittany-cartwright-boyfriend-split-082625-f6db1cfef0804949895dcbe5482d4a31.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/i3yO7KWh5oL6W3qHNuf41NtTgH0=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_byte